1) build

make 

copy the executable scanbd and config-file scanbd.conf to useful places

2) scanbd_dbus.conf

copy this file into the dbus system-bus configuration directory

3) inetd.conf

edit the saned-line to use scanbd as a wrapper

4) scanbd.conf

e.g.
sane-port stream tcp nowait saned.saned /usr/local/bin/scanbd scanbd -m -c /usr/local/etc/scanbd.conf


5) scripts

make some useful scripts

6) start the scanbd 

e.g.
/usr/local/scanbd -c /usr/local/etc/scanbd.conf